    "CommitMsg": "feat: in-app tile download, police→report history, fix sync clobber\n\nNew features:\n- DataDownloadScreen: pick state → download tiles/geocoder/routing from GitHub Releases\n- DataDownloadManager: OkHttp streaming, progress tracking, atomic writes, zip extraction\n- Integrated into Privacy Wizard (step 4) and Settings ('Download Map Data')\n- Storage warnings: amber \u003e2GB, red \u003e4GB with crash warning\n- Per-state remove button to delete downloaded data\n\nPolice sightings:\n- Filtered out of Threat History (shown in Report History instead)\n- Blue-themed PoliceDetectionItem cards with category, confidence %, coordinates\n- Blue strobe overlay kept for offline detection\n\nBuild fix:\n- syncSurveillanceData no longer auto-runs on build (Overpass timeouts clobber data)\n- Run manually: ./gradlew syncSurveillanceData\n- Speed cameras regenerated (1,616 features)",
